content:
Send a bulk SMS from a contact, employee, person account, or messaging user list view in a standard SMS channel. View your companyâ€™s sent broadcast messages in the Broadcast Messages tab.

Available in: Lightning Experience.

This article applies to: Standard SMS channels.

User permissions needed: Send One-to-Many Messages.

Standard SMS channels are scheduled for retirement. Upgrade to enhanced channels before February 14, 2026.

Broadcast messages can't be sent in SMS channels that use Omni-Channel flow routing.

Open a contact, employee, person account, or messaging user list view and select the recipients. Click Send Message.

Confirm sender numbers, give your message an internal name, select a messaging template, and review your message before sending.

To see sent broadcast messages, open the Broadcast Messages tab in the navigation menu.
title: Sending Bulk SMS with Service Cloud
